### Health check
GET http://localhost:8080/health

###

### Register — valid
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Akshad Jaiswal",
  "email": "akshad@examplee.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Register — missing name (422 validation error)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "akshad@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Register — invalid email format (422)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Akshad",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Register — password too short (422)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Akshad",
  "email": "akshad2@example.com",
  "password": "abc"
}

###

### Register — multiple errors at once (422)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "A",
  "email": "bademail",
  "password": "123"
}

###

### Login — valid (copy token for protected routes below)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "akshad@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login — missing email (422)
POST http://localhost:8080/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### List users — valid token
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get user — invalid UUID (400)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/not-a-uuid
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Create user — validation errors (422)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "",
  "email": "bademail"
}

###

### Update user — valid (replace UUID)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/users/REPLACE_WITH_UUID
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "Akshad Updated",
  "email": "akshad.updated@example.com"
}
